@chuuya#106771 Ja sam napravio odvojeni ViewSet:

```python
class UserViewSet(viewsets.ModelViewSet):
    queryset = get_user_model().objects.all().order_by("id")
    serializer_class = UserSerializer


class FileViewSet(viewsets.ModelViewSet):
    queryset = File.objects.all().order_by("identifier")
    serializer_class = FileSerializer


class NestedFileViewSet(viewsets.ModelViewSet):
    serializer_class = FileSerializer

    def get_queryset(self):
        return File.objects.filter(owner__id=self.kwargs["user_pk"])
```

I onda taj drugi viewset predaš kad radiš routanje.
